commit.message:
Revert "Convert from QRegExp to QRegularExpression"

This reverts commit e9877edb8ed8e722fb76f65320ae3766f9d92746.

The commit breaks search with Japanese characters due to some
differences between QRegExp and QRegularExpression. I'm working on a
fix, but revert for now to keep ToT clean.

Convert from QRegExp to QRegularExpression

QRegExp is deprecated in Qt6, so make the change in prevision of a
future update.

CMakeLists: require cmake >= 3.5

Compatibility for prior version will be dropped by cmake, so increase
the required version to the next minimally supported one.
CMakeLists: fix cmake warning
format CMakelists.txt files

add 'format' build target and reformat whole codebase using clang-format

Formatting for the whole project was simply horrendous. Add a basic
clang-format config and use it to make it a bit more pleasant to work
on.
Add support for copying multiple writings/readings to clipboard

Drop obsolete URIs for JMdict file downloaded by build system.

http://www.bcit-broadcast.com/monash/JMdict.gz no longer works at all.
ftp://ftp.net.usf.edu/pub/ftp.monash.edu.au/pub/nihongo/JMdict.gz is version from 2013-06-10.
Use https URI for JMdict file downloaded by build system.
Update KanjiVG version downloaded by build system to 20220427.
Support specifying custom paths to JMdict, kanjidic2, KanjiVG files.
1.2.2 release
Update transifex translations
Update SQLite to 3.40

gui/EntryListView: fix crash when removing lists with childs

The code in charge of removing the child nodes did not specify the
parent properly, resulting in an infinite recursion.

gui/EntryFormatter: fix crash when displaying a root list item

The sorting code chunk assumed the list hierarchy was not empty, which
causes a crash on root elements. Use the standard library reverse
algorithm instead of my poor code.

gui/EntryFormatter: display whole list hierarchy

Items in the list should display the whole hierarchy to their folder,
not just the last folder.
1.2.1 release
Update SQLite to 3.39.0
Update transifex translations

gui/EntriesViewHelper: fix printing of entries

When querying child nodes, don't forget to specify the parent! This bug
was introduced when replacing the obsolete QModelIndex::child() Qt
method.

Closes #246
1.2.0 release
Update transifex translations
Update SQLite to 3.38.5

CMakeLists: remove obsolete QT_DONT_USE_QTGUI

This was apparently a remnant of Qt4 and is not used in Qt5 at all.

Closes #253.
1.1.94 release
github/actions: update packages database before installing

gui/EntryDelegate: use QStyle to draw text and icons

The text color is better handled by the style ; use the dedicated
methods to make sure it remain consistent and legible with the style
of the user.

Closes #252.

Update kanjidic2 source

Github Actions seem to have trouble with non-https URLs?
1.1.93 release
